#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/areas.rst:6
msgid "Areas"
msgstr "Segmenti"

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/areas.rst:8
msgid ""
"The application window is always a rectangle on your desktop. It is "
"divided up into a number of re-sizable areas. An area contains the "
"workspace for a particular type of editor, like a 3D View Editor, or an "
"Outliner."
msgstr ""
"Glavni okvir aplikacije je u stvari jedan pravougaonik na radnoj površi. "
"Unutar aplikacije, ovaj okvir je podeljen na jedan ili više segmenata "
"promenljive veličine. Jedan segment predstavlja radni prostor za neki od "
"*montažera*, npr. 3D pregled ili Siže."

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/areas.rst:15
msgid "Arranging"
msgstr "Raspoređivanje"

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/areas.rst:17
msgid ""
"Blender uses a novel screen-splitting approach to arrange areas. The idea "
"is that you split up that big application window into any number of "
"smaller (but still rectangular) non-overlapping areas. That way, each area "
"is always fully visible, and it is very easy to work in one area and hop "
"over to work in another."
msgstr ""
"Blender upražnjava inovativni mehanizam za podelu glavnog okvira. Zamisao "
"je da razdelite glavni okvir na više manjih (takođe pravougaonih) "
"segmenata koji se ne preklapaju. Ovako svaki segment uvek vidite u celini, "
"a bez ikakvog truda možete raditi u jednom, a zatim se prebaciti na neki "
"drugi."

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/areas.rst:24
msgid "Changing the Size"
msgstr "Razvlačenje i sužavanje"

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/areas.rst:26
msgid ""
"You can resize areas by dragging their borders with :kbd:`LMB`. Simply "
"move your mouse cursor over the border between two areas, until it changes "
"to a double-headed arrow, and then click and drag."
msgstr ""
"Možete promeniti veličinu segmenata \"hvatanjem\" njihovih graničnika sa :"
"kbd:`LMB`. Jednostavno postavite kursor miša preko granične linije između "
"dva segmenta i kada ugledate dvosmernu strelicu, prevucite."

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/areas.rst:32
msgid "Splitting and Joining"
msgstr "Rezanje i kombinovanje"

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/areas.rst:35
msgid "Area Split Widget"
msgstr "Ručka za rezanje segmenata"

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/areas.rst:39
msgid ""
"In the upper right and lower left corners of an area are the area split "
"widgets, and they look like a little ridged thumb grip. It both splits and "
"combines areas. When you hover over it, your cursor will change to a cross "
"(✛)."
msgstr ""
"U gornjem desnom, kao i donjem levom uglu jednog segmenta naći ćete ručke "
"za pravljenje rezova, koje liče na rebraste hvataljke. One služe i rezanju "
"i spajanju segmenata. Kada pređete kursorom miša preko njih, kursor će "
"izgledati kao krst (✛)."

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/areas.rst:43
msgid ""
":kbd:`LMB` and drag it inward *split* the area. You define the direction "
"of that border by either dragging horizontally or vertically."
msgstr ""
":kbd:`LMB` i prevlačenjem ka \"unutra\" *režete* segment. Zavisno od "
"pokreta, možete napraviti vertikalni rez ili horizontalni rez."

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/areas.rst:46
msgid ""
"In order to *join* two areas :kbd:`LMB` click and drag the area splitter "
"outward. They must be the same dimension (width or height) in the "
"direction you wish to join. This is so that the combined area space "
"results in a rectangle."
msgstr ""
"Da bi *kombinovali* dva segmenta u jedan, :kbd:`LMB` i prevucite ka "
"\"spolja\". Neophodno je da su oba segmenta istih dimenzija (visina ili "
"širina), zavisno od pravca kombinovanja. Na ovaj način, rezultat će uvek "
"biti pravougaoni (četvorougaoni) segment. "

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/areas.rst:52
msgid "The Properties Editor is being merged \"over\" the Outliner."
msgstr "Glavni Panel koji se proširuje na račun Sižea."

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/areas.rst:54
msgid ""
"The area that will be closed gets a dark overlaid with an arrow. Now you "
"can select the area to be closed by moving the mouse over it."
msgstr ""
"Sadržaj segmenta koji će nestati biće zatamnjen, a preko toga videćete "
"indikator smera. Tada je trenutak da proširite jedan segment u prostor "
"nekog drugog prevlačenjem miša."

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/areas.rst:57
msgid ""
"Release the :kbd:`LMB` to complete the join. If you press :kbd:`Esc` or :"
"kbd:`RMB` before releasing the mouse, the operation will be aborted."
msgstr ""
"Otpustite :kbd:`LMB` miša da završite spajanje. Ako se predomislite, "
"pritisnite taster :kbd:`Esc` ili :kbd:`RMB` pre nego što otpustite :kbd:"
"`LMB` i spajanje će biti poništeno."

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/areas.rst:62
msgid "Area Options"
msgstr "Operacije nad segmentom"

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/areas.rst:64
msgid ":kbd:`RMB` on the border opens the *Area Options*."
msgstr ":kbd:`RMB` na graničnu liniju prikazuje *Operacije nad segmentom*."

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/areas.rst:67
msgid "Split Area"
msgstr "Rezanje segmenta"

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/areas.rst:67
msgid ""
"Shows an indicator line that lets you select the area and position where "
"to split. :kbd:`Tab` switches between vertical/horizontal."
msgstr ""
"Prikazuje indikator pomoću koga vršite odabir segmenta i poziciju reza. "
"Tasterom :kbd:`Tab` podešavate orijentaciju reza."

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/areas.rst:70
msgid "Join Areas"
msgstr "Kombinovanje segmenata"

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/areas.rst:70
msgid "Shows the join direction overlay."
msgstr "Prikazuje zatamnjenje i smer spajanja."

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/areas.rst:72
msgid "Confirm or cancel works as described above."
msgstr "Operacije možete otkazati na već opisan način."

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/areas.rst:76
msgid "Swapping Contents"
msgstr "Rokada sadržaja"

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/areas.rst:78
msgid ""
"You can swap the contents between two areas with :kbd:`Ctrl-LMB` on one of "
"the splitters of the initial area, dragging towards the target area, and "
"releasing the mouse there. The two areas do not need to be side-by-side, "
"though they must be inside the same window."
msgstr ""
"Možete izvršiti \"rokadu\" sadržaja dva segmenta pomoću :kbd:`Ctrl-LMB` na "
"nekoj od ručki za spajanje/rezanje početnog segmenta, zatim prevlačenjem "
"ka ciljnom segmentu, i otpuštanjem miša u okviru ciljnog segmenta. Ovo "
"možete izvesti i po dijagonali, ali ne i van glavnog prozora."

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/areas.rst:87
msgid "Duplicate Area into new Window"
msgstr "Kreiranje glavnog prozora sa postojećim segmentom"

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/areas.rst:89
#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/areas.rst:108
#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/areas.rst:136
msgid "Reference"
msgstr "Pregled"

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/areas.rst
msgid "Menu"
msgstr "Meni"

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/areas.rst:92
msgid ":menuselection:`View --> Duplicate Area into new Window`"
msgstr ":menuselection:`View --> Duplicate Area into new Window`"

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/areas.rst:94
msgid ""
"The new window is a fully functional window, which is part of the same "
"instance of Blender. This can be useful, e.g. if you have multiple "
"monitors."
msgstr ""
"Novokreirani okvir je u stvari novi prozor, ali se ne pokreće novi "
"program. Ovaj prozor pripada učitanom projektu; ovo je korisno za rad u "
"multi-monitor režimu."

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/areas.rst:97
msgid ""
"A new window can be created from :menuselection:`View --> Duplicate Area "
"into new Window`."
msgstr ""
"Novi okvir za Blender možete kreirati pomoću :menuselection:`View --> "
"Duplicate Area into new Window`."

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/areas.rst:99
msgid ""
"You can also create a new window from an existing area by :kbd:`Shift-LMB` "
"on the area splitter widget, then drag slightly."
msgstr ""
"Postoji i prečica za kreiranje novog okvira od postojećeg segmenta - :kbd:"
"`Shift-LMB` na ručku segmenta, zatim minimalni pokret miša."

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/areas.rst:102
msgid "The window can be closed with the OS *Close Window* button."
msgstr ""
"Ako imate više glavnih okvira, možete ih zatvoriti onako kako inače "
"zatvarate prozore."

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/areas.rst:106
msgid "Toggle Maximize Area"
msgstr "Režim jednog segmenta"

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/areas.rst:111
msgid ":menuselection:`View --> Toggle Maximize Area`"
msgstr ":menuselection:`View --> Toggle Maximize Area`"

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/areas.rst
msgid "Hotkey"
msgstr "Taster"

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/areas.rst:112
msgid ":kbd:`Ctrl-Up`, :kbd:`Shift-Spacebar`"
msgstr ":kbd:`Ctrl-Up`, :kbd:`Shift-Spacebar`"

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/areas.rst:114
msgid ""
"The maximized area fill the whole application window. It contains the Info "
"Editor and the select area."
msgstr ""
"Glavni okvir Blendera biće ispunjen jednim (odabranim) segmentom, iznad "
"koga će ostati traka Info Pregleda."

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/areas.rst:117
msgid ""
"You can maximize an area with the :menuselection:`View --> Toggle Maximize "
"Area` menu entry. To return to normal size use again menu entry, or :kbd:"
"`RMB` on the editors header and select *Maximize Area* and *Tiled Area* to "
"return. In the Info Editor header the *Back to Previous* button on the "
"right of the menus also returns to tiled areas."
msgstr ""
"Da bi se fokusirali na jedan određeni segment, koristite :menuselection:"
"`View --> Toggle Maximize Area` stavku. Da bi se vratili na standardni "
"pregled, aktivirajte istu stavku, ili :kbd:`RMB` na pod-traku montažera, i "
"odaberite *Maximize Area* i *Tiled Area*. U traci Info Pregleda, postoji "
"dugme *Back to Previous* desno od menija, koje vrši istu funkciju."

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/areas.rst:122
msgid ""
"A quicker way to achieve this is to use the shortcuts: :kbd:`Shift-"
"Spacebar`, :kbd:`Ctrl-Down` or :kbd:`Ctrl-Up` to toggle between maximized "
"and normal areas."
msgstr ""
"Najbrži način za menjanje režima prikaza segmenta zasigurno je "
"kombinacija :kbd:`Shift-Spacebar`, zatim :kbd:`Ctrl-Down` ili :kbd:`Ctrl-"
"Up`."

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/areas.rst:127
msgid ""
"The area your mouse is currently hovering over is the one that will be "
"maximized using the keyboard shortcuts."
msgstr ""
"Kad koristite tastere, operaciju vršite nad segmentom preko koga se nalazi "
"kursor miša."

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/areas.rst:134
msgid "Toggle Fullscreen Area"
msgstr "Režim prikaza segmenta"

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/areas.rst:139
msgid ":menuselection:`View --> Toggle Fullscreen Area`"
msgstr ":menuselection:`View --> Toggle Fullscreen Area`"

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/areas.rst:140
msgid ":kbd:`Alt-F10`"
msgstr ":kbd:`Alt-F10`"

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/areas.rst:142
msgid ""
"The fullscreen area contains only the main region. The headers visibility "
"can still be toggled with the shortcut. To exit the fullscreen move the "
"mouse to the top right corner of the area to reveal the return icon or use "
"the shortcut :kbd:`Alt-F10`."
msgstr ""
"Možete na brzinu razvući glavnu regiju nekog segmenta preko celog prozora. "
"Prečice za pod-trake i dalje važe. Za izlaz iz ovog režima, ciljajte mišem "
"na gornji desni ugao dok se ne pojavi dugme za vraćanje ili koristite "
"taster :kbd:`Alt-F10`."
